   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>What you brought is something that only <FONT color=#a82424>Priestesses of Darkness</FONT> can get.<BR>Since you managed to bring it, I should lay down my doubts.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-accepting-a" image="QN_Npc_eclairer.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-accepting-b" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Castia sighs)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>I never imagined I would meet <FONT color=#a82425>Eclair</FONT>'s son like this.<BR>The Goddess's will works in mysterious ways.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-accepting-acceptted" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Secret of Eclair$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1" image="QN_Npc_eclairer.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-a" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Eclair</FONT> was my senior. She was an outstanding <FONT color=#a82424>healer</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82425>guardian</FONT>.<BR>With her deep understanding of the darkness, she work hard to stop the nightmares from overflowing to the outside world and devoted her life to protect this place.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-b" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>It is actually forbidden for Priestesses of Darkness to give birth to a child of a human. But you were born, like a miracle. But Éclair's body must have been very different from a normal human's since she stayed here in the Boundary of Darkness for so long. So her son too...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-c" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What do you mean she refused it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>You must be affected by the Boundary of Darkness like your mother. In fact, you were fated to a lead a life that belonged neither to this place nor the bright world above. But Éclair refused that.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-d" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see… (You cannot remember anything)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR><FONT color=#a82425>Eclair</FONT> decided to risk going outside to take you to the brighter world.<BR>
She hoped you would live like an ordinary human and sent you to your father.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-e" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then what should I do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>But since you came back here, it looks like you can't lead a life as an ordinary human.<BR>This is destiny.... Or shall I say Goddess Altea's profound intentions…?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-class1" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Strong power...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>Well… I hope you accept your fate. You will never belong either to the dark world or the bright world…<BR>But as someone at the boundary, you will be able to attain much more powerful strength.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-g" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What's that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>A human like you will be able to use the power of the Guardians of Pledge.<BR>Though this is a really rare case, I'm sure you can become a <FONT color=#a82424>Guardian</FONT> or a <FONT color=#a82424>Crusader</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-h" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Guardians</FONT> take after Paladin's defence skills. They steal their enemies' attention and support their allies with various debuff attacks.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-l" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Crusaders</FONT> take after Paladin's attack skills. Using magical and physical attacks at the same time, they are capable of both wide area and focused attacks.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-j" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What's that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>Being able to use Éclair's healing powers is dangerous, yet really powerful for a human. Though this is a rare case, I'm sure you can become a <FONT color=#a82424>Saint</FONT> or an <FONT color=#a82424>Inquisitor</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-k" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Saints</FONT> take after Priest's secondary skills. They support their allies with relics and buffs that raise their allies' survival rate and damage dealing abilities.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-l" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Inquisitors</FONT> take after Priest's attack skills. They can deal wide area attacks with powerful light attribute attacks.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-m" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I can see her?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>You can choose your path and get stronger power.<BR>But before that, it would be good if you meet <FONT color=#a82424>Eclair</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-n" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Crest of Pledge?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>You must meet her. If you want to get strong power, you need to complete <FONT color=#a82424>Crest of Pledge</FONT>and put it in your body. And this only can be done by <FONT color=#a82425>Eclair</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-1-o" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>It is the product of strong will to live in Border of Darkness. Only Priestess of Darkness can make it. I can't put it in your body but I can help you to make it with several fragments from Priestess's Nightmare.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-1-o" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300424" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-2" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How can I get them?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>So <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>if you want to complete <FONT color=#a82424>Crest of Pledge</FONT>, you need to collect <FONT color=#a82425>depleted jewel fragments</FONT>.<BR>If your will is strong, it won't be difficult.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-2" image="QW_55.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia${action:Talk}<BR>You can get it from <FONT color=#a82424>East Ancient Armory</FONT>'s <FONT color=#a82424>Great Mimic Dalton</FONT>.<BR>Please hurry.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-3-a" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Here you are.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>You came back.<BR>Please bring them to me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n199_darklair_castia-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n199_darklair_castia-3-b" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Castia$<BR>I'll make Crest of Pledge for you. However, as I told you before, I'm just able to make it. It is impossible for me to put it in your body.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
